The paper discusses the use of automatic differentiation in machine learning, which is a subfield of computer science. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves numerical algorithms and optimization, which suggests categories such as cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) and cs.SC (Scientific Computing). The paper also discusses the implementation of automatic differentiation in software, which suggests categories such as cs.SE (Software Engineering). Finally, the paper involves the manipulation of mathematical functions, which suggests a category such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
